{
  "stem": "1511.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's late after the concert.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Come sleep with us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That night the Russian came with police and with, with, with dogs and with, with everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And wherever they had the address, as they pulled them all out, put all these people in-- in trains.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And trains where you-- where you-- when you buy cows, horses-- in trains like that, without nothing, just plain dirty.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they threw 'em all in there in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They gave them a lot of herring.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But they didn't give 'em water to drink.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I shouldn't-- I always obey to say that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because if wouldn't be for the Russian, a lot of people wouldn't be alive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But there was plenty going on in behind in Russia, too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I mean, Stalin did a lot of dirty tricks to the people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But then the other hand, the Russian people were very nice to us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Wherever we came, they took us in, they give us food, and they let us stay.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Of course, I always find Jewish families, and one help the other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I mean, what was going on in Germany is not a compare.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "On the other side, I mean, what it was divided in Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I don't call it Germany, it was still-- you know, but they took it over.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I can't say that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because if I say, maybe the government, I didn't know what was doing, what they have in behind.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they did a dirty joke.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took everybody out, whoever it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was a survivor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I survived because I was sleeping not at home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They couldn't find me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took them all to Siberia to [NON-ENGLISH] to-- the end, there where-- where there was no-- no life.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
